snippet.title: Stars Share What's On Their Watchlist For 2026
snippet.description:
Ferris Bueller's Day Off to Marty Supreme, film and television actors (and Bill Nye) reveal which mobies they're checking off their bucket list in 2026. Includes submissions from Ben Affleck, Holly Hunter, Kate Mulgrew, Matt Damon, Paul Giamatti, and more!
